{% call components.section("Style") -%}
  <p>
    Jump links are fixed on the page and follow a user as they scroll. It moves them to a section of content when the corresponding link is selected. It looks visually similar to <a href="../accordion">Open tabs</a>, the only difference is the uppercase label on top.
  </p>

