      <img src="{{ 'http://www.placehold.it/300x291' | url }}" alt="Example of a jump link">
      </div>
  {%- endcall %}

  <h3>Active indicator bar</h3>
  <p>A red indicator bar highlights what the active section is. It’s positioned on top of the anchor line, not adjacent.</p>

